{"tid":1614981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊：緊急法或宵禁令都會令香港國際形象大打折扣","createTime":"2019-10-03T03:01:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T03:31:28.000Z","uid":40667,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6c53b3683ced9a011c2a05e1c93721db4bad9d","tid":1614981,"uid":40667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:01:39.000Z","msg":"有報道指政府正研究推動各種更有效的方法止暴制亂，包括推行宵禁令。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊認為，宵禁令對香港人的影響非常大，如果可以選擇，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他個人寧願選擇引用緊急法。</span></span>但對引用緊急法仍有好大保留。至於引用緊急法延長拘留時間和訂立蒙面法是否可以考慮，湯家驊形容，是不可接受中比較可以接受的方案。不過，他認為這些做法只能爭取表面平靜，同時加深社會撕裂。但目前已沒有好的方法，只能選擇沒有那麼壞的解決方法。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊接受本台節目《千禧年代》訪問。他表示，10月1日發生開槍的事件後，開始懷疑自己的決定和立場，擔心遲早會發生第二宗，結果可能不會如今次的不幸中之大幸。他又說即使警方執法，市民仍會以身試法，推動任何政策和法律都不能解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊承認，引用緊急法或宵禁令都會令香港的國際形象會大打折扣，如要實施宵禁令，如何執行、罰則如何，市民會否接受，會否有更多無辜守法的市民受害等的問題，都不能簡單能處理。<br />\n<br />\n港大法律學院首席講師張達明認為，政府以嚴刑峻法解決問題，是用錯方法，如要真的實施宵禁令，影響會好大，希望政府能懸崖勒馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484001-20191003.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484001-20191003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7PDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=c85c5de3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1484001-20191003.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9db0dd5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1484001-20191003.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n緊急法 GO GO GO <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f69a71e423c8ea3d62fe21196662ee62a99503e1","tid":1614981,"uid":118665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:02:18.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978ba95d5264445a13fce80b219b7634e668aefe","tid":1614981,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:02:49.000Z","msg":"誰怕誰"},{"pid":"8390d062196be41c2ab08ae23806e6fcfb716208","tid":1614981,"uid":6833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:02:50.000Z","msg":"兩個都出哂佢啦"},{"pid":"3207529ba783c8785a508fbccc110c975ee7850e","tid":1614981,"uid":279236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:03:19.000Z","msg":"出得未啫屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"084d317c0432c674cbcde3120232e2e4a321b671","tid":1614981,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"Why not both"},{"pid":"a39d77a282b6adee75b8244c6e249480a73cb3ee","tid":1614981,"uid":322732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:04:23.000Z","msg":"湯渣又放毒藥出黎陰林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09b669231c9d3d4237f067c7d948198569d10e11","tid":1614981,"uid":261913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:04:26.000Z","msg":"咁大個仔第一次g持十一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"877a5e08ab6e260d99c33f612f5eb3a0a7b32b9c","tid":1614981,"uid":226956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:04:49.000Z","msg":"佢害少次香港人得唔得？"},{"pid":"6acc9427a904fb13e39e6fa71dc2e15cd272c567","tid":1614981,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">流浮山刀手呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5f919e422ee4ccad2dac1b5f10b5d916e71c22d7","tid":1614981,"uid":42751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T03:05:46.000Z","msg":"十一哥我地支持你"},{"pid